HEADWORD: spin the platter
<hw>spin the platter</hw></mhw>
<pos>n.</pos> <def>a game in which something round (as a plate) is spun
on edge and the name of a player is called; the named player must catch
the spinning object before it falls or pay a forfeit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spinule</ent>⟦br⟧
